{"tid":758873,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【唔怕得罪強國】越南准台商高掛台灣旗  免排華示威受攻擊","createTime":"2018-07-28T06:03:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T06:26:46.000Z","uid":184679,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"41e9e039517f6fccf178cc4ab1694ac9c6e56cac","tid":758873,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T06:03:25.000Z","msg":"越南曾在2014年爆發大規模的「513排華事件」，雖然當時許多越南人衝着中國工廠抗議，但由於多數人分不清楚台灣廠商與中國廠商，導致不少台商也跟着遭殃。但現在有台商指出，越南政府為了辨別台商與中國廠商，同意台商廠區可高掛青天白日滿地紅旗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180728&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=58496618\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180728%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D58496618&d=uBYLp38IdER8mI%2BiaMykebIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=10a4f42d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180728%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D58496618&h=d5b19cfd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180728&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=58496618</a>"},{"pid":"6862caf38df129a76dec04f369f2bcd3c026fbf6","tid":758873,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T06:04:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f86fa7f29476614f39b44705fa88864389c201","tid":758873,"uid":37528,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T06:04:48.000Z","msg":"算唔算第一個國家帶頭分開台灣同支那？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0897cd4e8b104ca20c046683ae743d704a66e708","tid":758873,"uid":65984,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T06:05:25.000Z","msg":"咁玩法大陸廠肯定掛哂台灣旗, 最後結果都係一樣"},{"pid":"0f335e2c00aa40d1de05efbb00b4040ad9eceaef","tid":758873,"uid":120678,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T06:05:28.000Z","msg":"越南好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4138837a0